title: Earl Thomas & 2020 Hype Champion Contenders
itunes:title: Earl Thomas & 2020 Hype Champion Contenders
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including the Ravens parting ways with Earl Thomas (10:10), Mike Williams being week to week (23:09), and a incident of 77 false positive Covid tests in the NFL (25:02). The heroes talk HYPE teams and who are hype champion contenders (33:24).
